Tatami Tests



 	This project provides functional test to tatami. It is consisted of Test Pages,
 	which is a bunch of GWT modules providing simple use cases, and HTMLUnit tests, which are run
 	against those pages.
 	
 	See the LICENSE files for licensing conditions. 
 	
 	Dependencies :
		- JUnit 3.x : http://www.junit.org/ 
		- HTMLUnit 2.3 : http://htmlunit.sourceforge.net/
		- Tatami : http://code.google.com/p/tatami/
		- TatamiTestUtils : http://code.google.com/p/tatami/
		- GWT : http://code.google.com/webtoolkit/
		
		Place htmlunit libs in the lib/htmlunit/ folder 
		and junit.jar,tatami.jar,tatamiTestUtil.jar in the lib folder, or modify the env.properties
		file according to your needs.
		
		Modify the env.properties file according to your gwt location.
	
	
	Build:
	
	Run ant on the tatami-tests.ant.xml file.
	
	 
	







